title: Patrick Falk
text: Patrick Falk (born 8 February 1980) is a German <a href="Association%20football">football</a> manager and former player. He made his debut on the professional league level in the <a href="Bundesliga">Bundesliga</a> for <a href="Eintracht%20Frankfurt">Eintracht Frankfurt</a> on 14 August 1999 when he came on as a substitute in the 67th minute in a game against <a href="SpVgg%20Unterhaching">SpVgg Unterhaching</a>.
